    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1937-12-16T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1937-12-16T00:00:00-05:00" n="908"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d908">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">893.01 Provisional/14</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">British Embassy</gloss> to the <gloss
                            type="to">Department of State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <p rend="center">
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Aide-Mémoire</hi>
                </p>
                <p>Numerous reports have reached His Majesty’s Government in the United Kingdom that
                    the Japanese intend almost immediately to recognize the autonomous
                    administration just set up in Peking. If they do, it will presumably be
                    necessary for the non-recognizing governments to withdraw all Diplomatic
                    Officers, leaving two or three Consular Officers to maintain contact with the
                    puppet regime. The Embassy guards may have to withdraw from Peking and the
                    question of their position at Tientsin, which would be under the same puppet
                    government, would require immediate consideration.</p>
                <p>His Majesty’s Government would be glad to learn as soon as possible what are the
                    intentions of the United States Government as regards both the Diplomatic Staff
                    and the military contingent maintained in North China.</p>
                <closer>
                    <dateline rendition="#left">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1937-12-16">December 16,
                            1937</date>.</dateline>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
